# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# SQL Database Analysis Tool — .gitignore
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── SECURITY: Never commit secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!backend/.env.example
!backend/app/.env.example
*.key
*.pem
*.cert
*.crt
secrets/
credentials/
backend/app/logs/
backend/app/exports/

# ── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
eggs/
parts/
var/
sdist/
develop-eggs/
.installed.cfg
lib/
lib64/
.eggs/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/
.python-version

# ── Testing & Coverage ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/
reports/
coverage.xml
*.cover
nosetests.xml
test-results/
junit*.xml

# ── Type checking ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.mypy_cache/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json
.pyre/
.pytype/

# ── Linting ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ruff_cache/

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
alembic/versions/*.pyc
db/data/

# ── Exports (generated files) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
exports/
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.pdf
reports/

# ── Docker ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.docker/

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
*.log.*
log/

# ── Node.js / Frontend ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.next/
out/
.nuxt/
dist/
.cache/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
.npm
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz
.pnp.*
frontend/.env
frontend/.env.local
frontend/.env.development
frontend/.env.production

# ── IDE & Editor ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# ── OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# ── Jupyter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints
*.ipynb

# ── Temporary files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup
*.orig

# ── Local state files ──
frontend/.connections.json
frontend/.active_session.json
frontend/user_settings.json
backend/scratch/
